    "Thermodynamic stability of a cosmological fluid is commonly assessed through the square of its effective sound speed, defined as",
    "In the context of the EUP-modified Friedmann equations, the expressions for pressure and energy density lead to a nontrivial but analytically tractable form of c 2 s.",
